287
00:19:01,220 --> 00:19:02,540
Your crown princess.

288
00:19:03,860 --> 00:19:05,580
His Majesty has given an imperial edict

289
00:19:05,740 --> 00:19:06,980
to document Miss Cui's daily life

290
00:19:07,140 --> 00:19:08,540
in the mansion

291
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:10,020
