307
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:03,420
And branch to which my lady belongs is called Wushui.

308
00:20:03,540 --> 00:20:05,340
It got prosperous because of our chief.

309
00:20:05,620 --> 00:20:06,180
My Lady is the only girl

310
00:20:06,260 --> 00:20:07,180
in her family,

311
00:20:07,300 --> 00:20:08,580
also the future crown princess.

312
00:20:08,700 --> 00:20:10,780
That's why she's got lots of birthday presents.

313
00:20:30,940 --> 00:20:32,180
Did you forget what I said?

314
00:20:41,100 --> 00:20:43,460
No formality inside the mansion.

315
00:20:43,940 --> 00:20:45,020
