319
00:20:51,100 --> 00:20:52,220
for anyone.

320
00:20:52,820 --> 00:20:53,820
After thinking it over.

321
00:20:54,940 --> 00:20:56,060
I think this

322
00:20:56,180 --> 00:20:57,340
might be suitable.

323
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:01,300
Open it and take a look

324
00:21:01,760 --> 00:21:02,860
before you decide whether you want it or not, okay?

325
00:21:18,020 --> 00:21:19,580
These are all the seals from the generals who surrendered to me

326
00:21:19,850 --> 00:21:21,580
after I left the Central State.

327
00:21:26,740 --> 00:21:28,420
I was gonna give it to my royal brother.

328
00:21:29,020 --> 00:21:30,300
But it's fine if I give it to you,

329
00:21:30,780 --> 00:21:32,260
