337
00:21:49,620 --> 00:21:51,020
I will make sure it's well-kept,

338
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:52,460
and protect it with my life.

339
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:29,060
We are about to send out our troops.

340
00:22:31,380 --> 00:22:32,260
Get ready.

341
00:22:32,620 --> 00:22:34,780
