344
00:22:38,300 --> 00:22:39,780
Yes.

345
00:22:40,900 --> 00:22:41,620
Your Highness.

346
00:22:42,940 --> 00:22:44,700
There is one more person to concern.

347
00:22:49,010 --> 00:22:51,180
Oh, and Shiyi.

348
00:22:53,530 --> 00:22:55,980
When we went for a battle before, we went without delay

349
00:22:56,380 --> 00:22:57,980
