440
00:29:15,210 --> 00:29:18,960
♫I'm full of love for you♫

441
00:29:18,420 --> 00:29:19,060
Watch out.

442
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:23,480
♫Waiting to unlock the years of time♫

443
00:29:19,860 --> 00:29:21,300
Are you injured? Let me see.

444
00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:23,700
I will go get the medicine.

445
00:29:23,780 --> 00:29:29,290
♫Our eyes will still be full of stars when we reunite♫

