00:29:30,290 --> 00:29:36,000
♫We will still promise with each other when we reunite♫

447
00:30:10,740 --> 00:30:11,260
What's up?

448
00:30:11,580 --> 00:30:12,500
You thought I was your master?

449
00:30:14,700 --> 00:30:15,740
