450
00:30:16,860 --> 00:30:18,180
Why didn't he come back to his mansion?

451
00:30:19,620 --> 00:30:20,420
He is wounded.

452
00:30:20,580 --> 00:30:21,420
In case of information leakage,

453
00:30:21,580 --> 00:30:22,700
he is temporarily recovering in the camp.

454
00:30:25,220 --> 00:30:25,820
Where are you going?

455
00:30:26,580 --> 00:30:27,380
The military camp.

456
00:30:29,060 --> 00:30:29,740
Did you forget it?

457
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:31,020
Your master doesn't allow you to go there.

458
00:30:31,660 --> 00:30:32,860
That's what he told me before he left.

459
00:30:32,980 --> 00:30:33,820
Now that he's back.

460
00:30:33,940 --> 00:30:34,780
Those words don't count.

461
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:37,980
All right.

462
00:30:38,260 --> 00:30:39,100
