464
00:30:40,340 --> 00:30:41,580
He shouldn't blame you.

465
00:30:55,860 --> 00:30:56,740
I'll take the bamboo slips.

466
00:30:56,860 --> 00:30:57,500
You take the books.

467
00:31:08,340 --> 00:31:10,540
