472
00:31:20,380 --> 00:31:21,140
Watch your step.

473
00:31:29,540 --> 00:31:30,740
Is the letter from Shouyang here?

474
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:50,900
Eleven.

475
00:31:56,220 --> 00:31:58,540
