476
00:32:08,020 --> 00:32:09,340
It's another year you haven't seen each other, isn't it?

477
00:32:09,500 --> 00:32:11,100
How long have we been away?

478
00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:12,620
Since we left the Western State,

479
00:32:13,020 --> 00:32:14,100
