483
00:32:27,740 --> 00:32:28,380
Master.

484
00:32:29,140 --> 00:32:30,180
I have prepared the provisions

485
00:32:30,300 --> 00:32:31,460
according to your order.

486
00:32:31,500 --> 00:32:31,900
Great.

487
00:32:32,220 --> 00:32:32,940
So tonight,

488
00:32:33,060 --> 00:32:34,140
you set out with the provisions

489
00:32:34,300 --> 00:32:35,180
to Shouyang.

490
00:32:35,420 --> 00:32:36,620
