494
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:41,900
Got it.

495
00:32:43,580 --> 00:32:45,060
Glad Shiyi is here today.

496
00:32:45,180 --> 00:32:46,500
Even if all of us were gone,

497
00:32:46,620 --> 00:32:47,940
