505
00:33:08,340 --> 00:33:09,580
Master won't allow us to make it public.

506
00:33:09,860 --> 00:33:11,940
It will get worse at night.

507
00:33:12,220 --> 00:33:13,660
So, you need to be extra careful.

508
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:16,580
Now Master is all yours.

509
00:33:17,620 --> 00:33:19,940
I'll also leave my brother to you.

510
00:33:21,060 --> 00:33:21,860
Don't worry.

511
00:33:22,060 --> 00:33:23,580
He will be okay as long as I am.

512
00:33:24,540 --> 00:33:26,500
Our master and I will be the same.

513
00:33:30,820 --> 00:33:32,180
Please take a good rest, Your Highness.

514
00:33:39,620 --> 00:33:40,540
Why are you here?

515
00:33:41,460 --> 00:33:42,540
I worry about you.

516
00:33:43,380 --> 00:33:45,180
Go take a rest in Xiaoyu's camp.

517
00:33:49,100 --> 00:33:50,380
You won't be of much help here.

518
00:33:50,580 --> 00:33:51,860
I can handle this.

519
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:54,740
Go ahead.

520
00:34:43,580 --> 00:34:44,540
Anything wrong, My Lady?

521
00:34:48,219 --> 00:34:49,020
Well...

522
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:52,820
I am afraid His Highness will blame that on me.

523
00:34:53,699 --> 00:34:54,900
Please.

524
00:34:56,540 --> 00:34:57,580
All right, all right.

525
00:35:54,460 --> 00:35:55,460
If he keeps sleeping,

526
00:35:55,780 --> 00:35:56,980
