540
00:37:28,460 --> 00:37:29,340
Medic.

541
00:37:31,060 --> 00:37:31,780
Your Highness.

542
00:37:32,500 --> 00:37:33,580
I was being careless

543
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:34,660
