551
00:38:02,500 --> 00:38:03,740
Why are you so worried?

552
00:38:38,620 --> 00:38:39,620
What do you want?

553
00:38:40,700 --> 00:38:43,100
No matter what you say,

554
00:38:43,820 --> 00:38:45,460
I am staying.

555
00:38:47,540 --> 00:38:48,260
You have made up your mind?

556
00:38:52,100 --> 00:38:53,140
These days,

557
00:38:53,420 --> 00:38:53,980
I am afraid

558
00:38:54,060 --> 00:38:55,660
